<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Divya Darshan | Experience the Divine</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --navy: #081A39;
            --gold: #FFD700;
            --gold-dark: #ccac00;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: white;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* 1. Glassy Sticky Navbar */
        nav {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 15px 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .logo {
            color: var(--navy);
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 35px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--navy);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links a:not(.signup-btn)::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            background: var(--gold-dark);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

        .signup-btn {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            color: var(--gold) !important;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        /* 2. Hero Section Flex Layout */
        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 80px 7%;
            gap: 60px;
            min-height: 80vh;
        }

        .hero-text {
            flex: 1.2;
            min-width: 320px;
        }

        .hero-text h1 {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.1;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .highlight { 
            color: var(--gold);
            text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .hero-text p {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            opacity: 0.85;
            margin: 30px 0;
            max-width: 580px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .btn-yellow {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #ffb700);
            color: var(--navy);
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: 0.4s;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn-yellow:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.35);
        }

        /* 3. Side Content (Glass Quote & Cards) */
        .side-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 350px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 35px;
        }

        .quote-box {
            background: var(--glass);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-style: italic;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--gold);
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .temple-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            transition: 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        .temple-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02);
        }

        .image-container {
            height: 160px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #eee;
        }

        .image-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: 0.6s;
        }

        .temple-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.15); }

        .card-info {
            padding: 18px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-info h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--navy);
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .card-info p {
            margin: 6px 0 0;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        /* 4. Footer Wisdom */
        .wisdom-footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 60px 7% 100px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero-section { text-align: center; justify-content: center; padding-top: 50px; }
            .hero-text p { margin: 30px auto; }
            .btn-group { justify-content: center; }
            .quote-box { order: -1; } /* Quote mobile pe upar aayega */
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            nav { padding: 15px 5%; }
            .nav-links { display: none; } /* Mobile menu toggle handle manually if needed */
            .hero-text h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo">ॐ DIVYA DARSHAN</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/book">Book Puja</a>
            <a href="/history">My Bookings</a>
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/signup" class="signup-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Experience <br> the Divine, <br> <span class="highlight">Anywhere</span></h1>
            <p>Bridging the gap between faith and distance. Join thousands of devotees in sacred rituals and live darshan from India's holiest temples, directly from your home.</p>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <a href="/book" class="btn-yellow">Start Darshan</a>
                <a href="/explore" class="btn-yellow" style="background: none; border: 2px solid white; color: white;">Explore Temples</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="side-content">
            <div class="quote-box">
                "When you step into a temple, you step into peace, faith, and divine energy."
            </div>

            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="temple-card">
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1627894483216-2138af692e32?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600" alt="Kashi Vishwanath">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h3>Kashi Vishwanath</h3>
                        <p>Varanasi, UP</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="temple-card">
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRidsKJL6jZ4AI4sdXqO9HfVwgZZwLu2E1pTg&s" alt="Somnath Mandir">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h3>Somnath Mandir</h3>
                        <p>Gujarat</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="temple-card">
                    <div class="image-container">
                        <img src="https://www.chardhamtour.in/assets/images/tourism/kedarnath/Kedarnath-Temple.webp" alt="Kedarnath Dham">
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h3>Kedarnath</h3>
                        <p>Uttarakhand</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wisdom-footer">
        <div class="quote-box" style="max-width: 650px; border-left: none; border-bottom: 5px solid var(--gold); background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.03);">
            <span style="color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 0.8rem;">SPIRITUAL WISDOM</span>
            "True Darshan is not just seeing God, it is feeling the divine within yourself and everything around you."
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>